fr.reflexe.viewshell.api.activation

Annotation Type ProvideService


  • @Documented
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=TYPE_USE)
public @interface ProvideService
    Declares a service that may be registered (published) when the service activator is instantiated.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    REFLEXE Technologies
    See Also:
    ActivationServices.provide()

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      Class<?> type
      Specifies the interface used to register (publish) the service.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      Implementation[] implementation
      Defines implementations of the specified type to be automatically instantiated and registered along with the service activator.

    • Element Detail

      • type

        public abstract Class<?> type
        Specifies the interface used to register (publish) the service.
        Returns:
        the registered service type.
        Since:
        1.0

      • implementation

        public abstract Implementation[] implementation
        Defines implementations of the specified type to be automatically instantiated and registered along with the service activator. Such implementations must define a public constructor accepting an associated instance of IServiceActivator. They will be automatically unregistered when the service activator is disposed of, without any direct notification.
        Returns:
        0..n implementation declarations.
        Since:
        1.0
        Default:
        {}
